A 3D scene of the Pyramids of Giza. The first and the oldest of the seven World Wonders, coded in c for OpenGL, that took me about 3 hours to finish.

I did not use any of the GLUT canned objects.

Key bindings
  m          Toggle between perspective and orthogonal
  +/-        Changes field of view for perspective
  a          Toggle axes
  arrows     Change view angle
  y/h 	     Zoom in and out
  0          Reset view angle
  ESC        Exit

make
run ./hw2
